snippet.title: 9 Lives To Defend - Trailer (alpha version)
snippet.description:
WishList now on Steam
https://cutt.ly/9LivesToDefend_Steam

The life of a cat has never been so eventful! In "9 Lives to Defend" you assume the role of Loki, a brave cat who needs to protect the house from invaders while its parents are away on vacation. With only nine lives, your survival skills will be tested against hordes of enemies in a frenetic bullet hell. Build unique matches using cards that only a clever kitten could wield. Play with different versions of Loki from other lives, and evolve your special abilities to fight this war like a true feline warrior ^.^
